abstract: The president’s picked-for-television defense team avoids a ratings “Death Valley,” then gets hit by a Bolton from the blue.
snippet: The president’s picked-for-television defense team avoids a ratings “Death Valley,” then gets hit by a Bolton from the blue.
lead_paragraph: President Trump, reportedly, wanted a telegenic team to make the case for him at his impeachment trial. But the biggest star in the Senate chamber on the first full day of his defense on Monday was The Man Who Wasn’t There.

headline_main: Trump Impeachment: A Dramatic Day, Everywhere but at the Podium

abstract: As Bernie Sanders exudes confidence in his ability to win next week's Iowa caucuses, his moderate rivals are struggling with how — and whether — to directly take on the progressive Vermont senator who some Democrats worry won't be able to defeat President Donald Trump.
snippet: As Bernie Sanders exudes confidence in his ability to win next week's Iowa caucuses, his moderate rivals are struggling with how — and whether — to directly take on the progressive Vermont senator who some Democrats worry won't be able to defeat P...
lead_paragraph: CEDAR FALLS, Iowa — As Bernie Sanders exudes confidence in his ability to win next week's Iowa caucuses, his moderate rivals are struggling with how — and whether — to directly take on the progressive Vermont senator who some Democrats worry won't be able to defeat President Donald Trump.
headline_main: Democrats Struggle With How Directly to Knock Sanders
headline_print_headline: Democrats Struggle With How Directly to Knock Sanders

abstract: The establishment doesn’t have the credibility to stop the surging Sanders movement.
snippet: The establishment doesn’t have the credibility to stop the surging Sanders movement.
lead_paragraph: A half-hour before a Bernie Sanders rally on Saturday night in Iowa, a line snaked around the nearly 900-seat Ames City Auditorium, but no one else was being let in: The theater was full.
